#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn3.16"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn3.16:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn3.16:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga "
msgstr "2. Childless "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 16. Mallikāsutta → dhītusuttaṃ (bj, s1-3, pts2) | dhitā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn3.16:0.3"
msgid "16. Mallikāsutta "
msgstr "16. A Daughter "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.86, pts2ed1.194, sc1
msgctxt "sn3.16:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn3.16:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho rājā pasenadi kosalo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. "
msgstr "Then King Pasenadi of Kosala went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to one side. "

msgctxt "sn3.16:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho aññataro puriso yena rājā pasenadi kosalo tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā rañño pasenadissa kosalassa upakaṇṇake ārocesi: "
msgstr "Then a man went up to the king and whispered in his ear, "

msgctxt "sn3.16:1.4"
msgid "“mallikā, deva, devī dhītaraṃ vijātā”ti. "
msgstr "“Your Majesty, Queen Mallikā has given birth to a daughter.” "

msgctxt "sn3.16:1.5"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, rājā pasenadi kosalo anattamano ahosi. "
msgstr "When this was said, King Pasenadi was disappointed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn3.16:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā rājānaṃ pasenadiṃ kosalaṃ anattamanataṃ viditvā tāyaṃ velāyaṃ imā gāthāyo abhāsi: "
msgstr "Then, knowing that King Pasenadi was disappointed, on that occasion the Buddha recited these verses: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn3.16:3.1"
msgid "“Itthīpi hi ekacciyā, "
msgstr "“Well, some women are better than men, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.16:3.2"
msgid "seyyā posa janādhipa; "
msgstr "O ruler of the people. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.16:3.3"
msgid "Medhāvinī sīlavatī, "
msgstr "Wise and virtuous, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.16:3.4"
msgid "sassudevā patibbatā. "
msgstr "a devoted wife who honors her mother in law. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn3.16:4.1"
msgid "Tassā yo jāyati poso, "
msgstr "And when she has a son, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.16:4.2"
msgid "sūro hoti disampati; "
msgstr "he becomes a hero, O lord of the land. "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: subhagiyā → subhariyā (s1-3, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "sn3.16:4.3"
msgid "Tādisā subhagiyā putto, "
msgstr "The son of such a blessed lady "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.16:4.4"
msgid "rajjampi anusāsatī”ti. "
msgstr "may even rule the realm.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
